That covers the entire CI/CD lifecycle: source → build → test → security → artifact → deploy → release → observe, plus the supporting infrastructure, environments, secrets, GitOps, and the tool ecosystem. The highest-leverage areas for daily work are pipeline-as-code, build/test automation, deployment strategies, secrets handling, and feedback/observability.